Message: Fix bug where process instance search criteria was fetching all document field values that match criteria for pinned fields rather than just those that have the pinned attributes on the field. What was happening is although we filtered the documents down based on fields with attributes; it still fetched all document field values. Retained the performance gain and fixed search to not include all field values; but only those with attributes.
